<p><img src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4131/5119458294_1a090287cc.jpg\" width=\"152\" height=\"410\" align=\"right\"/>‘A helicopter does not want to fly. It is maintained in the air by a variety of forces and controls, working in opposition to each other’.</p>
<ul><li><a href=\"http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=JTiLJeCOsfsC&pg=PA4&dq=helicopter+does+not+want+to+fly.+It+is+maintained+in+the+air+by+a+variety+of+forces+and+controls,+working+in+oppos&hl=en&ei=s5vHTL63HI_6sAOsntiEDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CDkQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q&f=false\" target=\"_blank\">Harry Reasoner</a></li>
</ul><p>‘The Apache helicopter pilots killed both Iraqi men after being advised by a US military lawyer that they could not surrender to an aircraft and therefore remained valid targets.’</p>
<ul><li><em><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/oct/22/iraq-war-logs-apache-insurgents-surrender\" target=\"_blank\">The Guardian</a></em>, 22 October 2010</li>
</ul><p>‘Fuck the ghetto bird.’</p>
<ul><li><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sRarzsKY8pw\" target=\"_blank\">Ice Cube</a></li>
</ul></blockquote>
<p>A white flag will not save you.</p>
<p>A nexus of blood-hungry lawfare and weaponised uncanny (that everyday bad miracle of ruling-class antigravity).</p>
<blockquote>
<p>‘[M]ankind being controlled and directed by spiritually unconscious or dead men would be in the position of a rushing airliner with an unconscious or dead crew in the control cabin.’</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Who the fuck do you think is flying this thing? The disavowal, the pretence at a warning, fools no one. This <em>is</em> the <a href=\"http://www.fatheralexander.org/booklets/english/invisible_encounter_sikorsky.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Invisible Encounter</a>. It’s happening right now. The angel of history is hovering overhead, drawing a bead, locking and loading.</p>
<p>So: <em><a href=\"http://www.socialistworker.co.uk/art.php?id=11476\" target=\"_blank\">Black Hawk down</a></em>.</p>" "http://chinamieville.net/post/1422766838" (19657 18412) new 2 nil nil ((title nil "
