<p><em>Non à la réforme</em>.</p>" "http://chinamieville.net/post/1368031567" (19648 40305) new 5 nil nil ((title nil "Unintended consequence of the BBC’s hunt for a local to...") (description nil "<embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"http://chinamieville.net/swf/audio_player.swf?audio_file=http://www.tumblr.com/audio_file/1368031567/tumblr_lanp81OGiS1qaycwg&color=FFFFFF\" height=\"27\" width=\"207\" quality=\"best\"></embed><br/><br/><p>Unintended consequence of the BBC’s <a href=\"http://news.bbc.co.uk/today/hi/today/newsid_9113000/9113269.stm\" target=\"_blank\">hunt</a> for a local to diss the Marseilles strikes? </p>
